    <entry>
      <title>22-4-26</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/26/22-4-26/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/26/22-4-26/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在insmod和rmmod时候想用printk打印调试，但是无论怎么设置等级：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;8 4 1 7&quot;</span> &gt; /proc/sys/kernel/printk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也没用啊，查了半天发现printk这个打印无法出现在<strong>伪终端</strong>（如远程终端）上，只能你给linux开发板连显示器，然后就会显示，那我差点就放弃。最后在万能的**<a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2170403/printk-showing-in-message-log-but-not-in-terminal-for-any-kernel-log-level">stackoverflow</a>**找到了勉强解决的方法，就是单独给printk一个terminal来让他只打印printk的log</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dmesg -wH &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>甚至还可以只打印单独的log类型，如下只打印<strong>KERN_EMERG</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dmesg -wH | grep ERR &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
